{"id":626,"parent_id":0,"book_id":8,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":626,"title":"Holy One of Israel","subtitle":"","short_title":"Holy One of Israel","uri":"/scriptures/bd/holy-one-of-israel","content":[["div",{"id":"t1","uri":"/scriptures/bd/holy-one-of-israel.t1","order":".000.1620"},[".title","Holy One of Israel"],["div",{"id":"p1","uri":"/scriptures/bd/holy-one-of-israel.p1","order":".000.1621"},"A name for the Savior used 34 times in the Old Testament, most frequently by Isaiah, who cites it 28 times (27 times in the book of Isaiah and once in",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/19.22"},"2 Kgs. 19:22"],"). It appears three times in the Psalms (",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/71.22"},"71:22"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/78.41"},"78:41"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/89.18"},"89:18"],"), twice in Jeremiah (",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/50.29"},"50:29"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/51.5"},"51:5"],"), and once in Ezekiel (",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/39.7"},"39:7"],"). Some references in Isaiah are",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/1.4"},"1:4"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/5.19"},"5:19"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/12.6"},"12:6"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/30.11-12,15"},"30:11–12, 15"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/48.17"},"48:17"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/60.14"},"60:14"],". The term is used frequently in the Book of Mormon, especially in 1 and 2 Nephi. The Holy One of Israel is identified as Christ in",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/25.29"},"2 Ne. 25:29"],"."]]],"refs":null}
